note.note-paragraph:
In this subclass, the following terms or expressions are used with the meaning indicated:
- "handling" includes processing or transporting of data;
- "data processing equipment" means an association of an electric digital data processor classifiable under group G06F7/00 , with one or more arrangements classifiable under groups G06F1/00 to G06F5/00 and G06F9/00 to G06F13/00 .
